<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>KYC Approval Confirmation</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333333; background-color: #f4f4f4;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff;">
        <!-- Header -->
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 30px 30px 20px 30px; text-align: center; background: #4a6cf7;">
                <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;">KYC Approved Successfully!</h1>
            </td>
        </tr>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 30px;">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 16px;">Dear {{user.first_name}} {{user.last_name}},</p>
                
                <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 16px;">We are pleased to inform you that your KYC verification has been successfully approved. Your account is now verified and you can continue using the platform according to your subscription plan.</p>
                
                <div style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;">
                    <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #4a6cf7; font-size: 18px;">Next Steps</h3>
                    <p style="margin: 15px 0 0 0; font-size: 15px;">
                        To access all features, please ensure you have an active subscription plan.
                    </p>
                </div>
                
                <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-size: 16px;">You can now log in to your account and explore the features available in your current plan.</p>
                
                <a href="{{loginUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 30px; background-color: #4a6cf7; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; margin: 10px 0;">Login to Your Account</a>
                
                <p style="margin: 20px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666666;">If you did not initiate this request, please contact our support team immediately.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px 30px; text-align: center; background: #f9f9f9; font-size: 14px; color: #666666;">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">© {{currentYear}} Your Company Name. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #999999;">This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
